record_data.record_title: Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources
record_data.record_plain_text:
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
Montour, LLC ( Montour ) provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ( Reactive Supply Service ) from various generating units in the PPL Zone to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ( PJM ). This Rate Schedule consists of two separate tariff rate sections, one for each generating unit, and sets forth Montour s revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Supply Service to PJM within the PPL Zone consistent with Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff.
Montour Unit 1
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $947,615.45.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $947,615.45 / 12 = $78,967.95.
Montour Unit 2
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $793,989.65.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $793,989.65 / 12 = $66,165.80.
